1. *Pijem* vodu svako jutro. (I drink water every morning.)
2. Često *pije* alkohol. (He often drinks alcohol.)
3. Ona je *pila* kafu pre nego što je otišla. (She drank coffee before she left.)
4. Oni su *pili* pivo uveče. (They drank beer in the evening.)
5. Mi smo *pili* sokove pre treninga. (We drank juices before the training.)
6. *Pijem* čaj uvek kada budem umorna. (I drink tea whenever I'm tired.)
7. Oni su *pili* vino pre nego što su otišli. (They drank wine before they left.)
8. Uvek *pijem* samo jednu vrstu soka. (I always drink only one type of juice.)